{"tid":472653,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[相認]patpat生左5蚊銀咁大粒瘡","createTime":"2017-11-18T12:32:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-04T00:50:57.000Z","uid":105485,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"d7a04f8ff9317ffa46f86216bb5d7e5343a15968","tid":472653,"uid":105485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T12:32:33.000Z","msg":"事源係幾日前右腳大脾近patpat深溝既位置生左粒暗瘡, 夜嘛嘛手痕就按左啲膿出黎, 咁就訓教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點知惡夢就開始 <br />\n過兩日就開始頭暈發燒, 粒暗瘡變到5蚊銀咁大粒, 周圍實的的, 按有膿同血水出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n痛住返工 每行一步就磨粒瘡一下 行到好似老江湖咁先冇事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一朝早就去左診所睇症, 話發炎比左啲抗生素同退燒止痛加盒藥膏就打發左我<br />\n<br />\n訓到琴晚愈燒愈勁 粒瘡頭變左黑色 <br />\n爬文啲巴打(1)入院開刀(2)等熟按爆<br />\n<br />\n最後飛的入左急症 排左幾粒鐘<br />\n個醫生就叫我反轉 要探肛 搽左啲ky就一野隊入黎 好彩係靚女醫生 我個處咁就冇左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上左病房訓訓下有個醫生黎抽血吊鹽水 叫我反轉又探一下&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再訓訓下又拍醒我叫我反轉再探多一下<br />\n其實係咪真係要探咁多下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  最緊要係探完勁急屎&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n轉個頭就入左手術室全身麻醉<br />\n訓醒竟然有個同齡絲打護士同我傾計 天使一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 快啲入黎相認<br />\n<br />\n同埋天使話比我知上一個做手術既男仔係同我一樣, 邊有咁岩架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有經驗巴絲可以分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a720d681c078d3f5fad4a688b11948970c2572d9","tid":472653,"uid":157039,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T12:35:28.000Z","msg":"圖呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20fb0be46922c7944fcf3f8623e3da7846b8e5c6","tid":472653,"uid":32577,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T12:36:34.000Z","msg":"雖然唔想講真相俾你知，但係你有知情權。。。。其實你已經死左 呢度係地獄界連登"},{"pid":"8590793aa9518197bbedfe82e7818d85273a28cb","tid":472653,"uid":153109,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T12:37:03.000Z","msg":"你係咪我同事？<br />\n尋日我同事都屎忽生瘡 仲要兩粒<br />\n同埋自己㩒爆左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc730c048b4f174a889b80bc6db0852083771643","tid":472653,"uid":30022,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T12:39:17.000Z","msg":"呢隻好似係叫漏管"},{"pid":"2ec04ed7f2dded9eb630838d31a71ac4fc0958d9","tid":472653,"uid":139139,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T12:43:43.000Z","msg":"證明你個屎忽好撚污糟囉，<br />\n死基佬。"},{"pid":"c6ab36c899afc5b2cb06b6b767bde7ae88ed926d","tid":472653,"uid":105485,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T12:50:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>圖呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/18/205013_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b